class=\"punctuation definition arguments end js\"><span>)</span></span></span><span class=\"punctuation terminator statement js\"><span>;</span></span><span>&#xA0;</span><span class=\"comment line double-slash js\"><span class=\"punctuation definition comment js\"><span>//</span></span><span>[[0,1,2],&#xA0;[0,2,3],&#xA0;...]</span><span>&#xA0;</span></span></span></div>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"license\">License</h2>\n<p>MIT, see <a href=\"http://github.com/vorg/geom-triangulate/blob/master/LICENSE.md\">LICENSE.md</a> for details.</p>\n"}